metadata.name: Heart condition
metadata.description:
This is where everything started and this is where everything  will end.
This precant is most pure one! There are no others like him! He will do anything to guide and help his observer. Name of the Precant is
Berika and his driving force is fire.

LYRICS
"Why do I need the heart in the chest if it doesn't burn like candle 
with the love of friend"

Tattoo on observers hand ( Old  Georgian letters ) 
 "I  am going to  kiss you in those areas where it will 
make you blush , not me."
